cc:Work.dc:title: Catalog of elliptic curves
cc:Work.dc:description:
Catalog of elliptic curves / Catalogue de courbes elliptiques: y³=x²+ax+b [-3,3]x[-3,3] Generated with / Généré avec Mathematica:
p = GraphicsArray[ Table[ContourPlot[y^2 == x^3 + a x + b, {x, -3, 3}, {y, -3, 3}, FrameTicks -> None], {a, -2, 1}, {b, -1, 2}]] xml = XML`SVG`GraphicsToSymbolicSVG[p]; Export["file.svg", xml, "XML"]
